      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Mated to a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox, the drivetrain maintains exceptional mechanical integrity. The chassis has been addressed with rear subframe reinforcement\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014and features refreshed bushings for precise turn-in. Equipped with a factory limited-slip differential and a high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling, this specimen offers a visceral, analog driving experience. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing service, ensuring the valvetrain and bottom end are track-ready. A true driver\u2019s car in solid operational form.",
